    <refpurpose>Bus Service Manager</refpurpose>
  </refnamediv>

  <refsect1>
    <title>Description</title>
    <para>The <command>org.bus1.administrator</command> is the central
    component of the running system. It keeps a direct connections to all
    services which are needed to control a running system. During bootup,
    it installs the service configurations in the
    <citerefentry><refentrytitle>org.bus1.activator</refentrytitle><manvolnum>1</manvolnum></citerefentry>,
    which is responsible to execute the services on-demand. The
    <command>org.bus1.administrator</command> activates and configures
    the services and maintains the overall system state according to
    its task.</para>
  </refsect1>

